title: Alternative Medicine (CAM) in the World - What is silenced
description: A comprehensive, scientifically focused set of texts and findings on the global state of complementary and alternative medicine (CAM), primarily from leading foreign sources (WHO, WHA, EU, Council of Europe, NATO, Cochrane, PubMed, EUROCAM, CAMbrella, and others) and JOSEF ZEZULKA BIOTRONICS - a new CAM field from the Czech Republic.
